It is also known as Bulk Processing
When you have a large amount of data and you want to process at one time, that is Called Batch Processing/Bulk Processing

Spring Batch:
1. It is Light weight batch framework based on Spring
2. It is used for High Volume Batch Processing(Means Millions of Records)
3. Various I/O Options - JSON, XML, SQL databases etc

    Source -----> Spring Batch  ---> Target

    Source/target can be any thing (CSV, Database, JSON)

4. Easy to manage, Start/Stop/Restart
5. Retry or Skip Mechanism